two_title: For this is now our 120th month
wishText: Hoping for more happy times to share through this lifetime with you
text1: Or roughly 522 weeks, 3650 days, 87.6K hours... Nevertheless, I will never get tired counting.
text2: I could have just done that but maybe not this time :D
outroText: Okay, now here's a poem I made for you :*
